CustomField.description: This option allows you to display more details in the drop down list when selecting the Shipmate Preference in the Shipping Wizard. This drop down list only appears on Preference Section of the Shipping Wizard if you have more than one Shipmate Preference.

CustomField.label: Detailed View - Shipmate Preference List
